# PATCH: 0003-default-password-banner
# WHY: Bo cai dat admin mac dinh admin/quickwin123 (yeu cau goc) — bat buoc nhac
#      nguoi dung doi ngay lan dau (plan 7.3). Banner canh bao mau cam hien khi user
#      la admin va chua bam "da doi/dismiss" (localStorage openitms_default_pwd_ack).
# WHAT: web/src/App.vue — them 1 v-alert (sau banner boltdb co san) +
#      computed showDefaultPasswordWarning + data defaultPasswordDismissed +
#      methods openChangePassword/dismissDefaultPasswordWarning. Chi frontend,
#      KHONG dung backend (route doi password /users/{id}/password da co san).
#      Rebase: neu App.vue doi, chen lai 1 v-alert trong v-main dau + 1 computed +
#      2 method. Khong co i18n key moi (text song ngu inline nhu banner boltdb goc).
# SPEC: docs/L2-specs/core-patches/0003-default-password-banner.md
# BASELINE: v2.18.16
#
diff --git a/web/src/App.vue b/web/src/App.vue
index d1083a4..a70c921 100644
--- a/web/src/App.vue
+++ b/web/src/App.vue
@@ -560,6 +560,29 @@
           <v-icon class="ml-2">mdi-open-in-new</v-icon>
         </v-btn>
       </v-alert>
+      <v-alert
+        type="warning"
